---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Help Center - AIVancePro"
  description="AIVancePro Help Center. FAQ, contact and technical support for the fitness coaching app."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/en/support/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/support/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/support/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/support/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .page-header { padding: 9rem 2rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-card), var(--bg)); }
      .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .page-header p { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .content { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 2rem 4rem; }
      .content h2 { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-900); margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .content p, .content li { color: var(--gray-700); font-size: 0.95rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .content ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
      .content strong { color: var(--gray-900); }
      .content a { color: var(--blue); }
      .contact-box { background: var(--gray-50); border: 1px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
      .contact-box p { margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
      .faq-section h2 { font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--gray-900); }
      .faq-list { max-width: 700px; }
      .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200); }
      .faq-question { width: 100%; background: none; border: none; text-align: left; padding: 1.5rem 0; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gray-900); cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-family: inherit; transition: color 0.2s; }
      .faq-question:hover { color: var(--blue); }
      .faq-question svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--gray-400); transition: transform 0.3s; flex-shrink: 0; }
      .faq-item.open .faq-question svg { transform: rotate(180deg); }
      .faq-answer { max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.3s ease; }
      .faq-answer-inner { padding: 0 0 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.7; }
      .faq-answer-inner ol { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .faq-answer-inner ol li { margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
      .faq-item.open .faq-answer { max-height: 300px; }
      .back { display: inline-block; margin-top: 2rem; color: var(--gray-500); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
      .back:hover { color: var(--gray-900); }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
          .page-header { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 1.5rem; }
          .page-header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Help Center</h1>
      <p>We are committed to providing the best possible experience for our users. If you encounter any issues or have questions, please use the resources below.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="content">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <div class="contact-box">
          <p><strong>By email:</strong> <a href="mailto:aivancepro@gmail.com">aivancepro@gmail.com</a></p>
          <p style="color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 0.85rem;">Our team typically responds within 24 to 48 hours.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;"><strong>Support form:</strong> <a href="https://forms.gle/F2NVKGcma7Y4auQc8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Open the form</a></p>
          <p style="color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 0.85rem;">Please provide as much detail as possible (device model, operating system version, and steps to reproduce the issue).</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-section">
          <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
          <div class="faq-list">
              <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                      The app won&#8217;t launch or displays a blank screen. What should I do?
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">
                      <ol>
                          <li>Make sure you have installed the latest version available on the App Store or Google Play.</li>
                          <li>Check your Internet connection (Wi-Fi or cellular).</li>
                          <li>Try force-closing and restarting the app.</li>
                      </ol>
                  </div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="faq-item">
                  <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                      How can I request the deletion of my data or my account?
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 11.168l3.71-3.938a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.5a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0l-4.25-4.5a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                  </button>
                  <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">You can request the deletion of your account directly in the app settings or by contacting us at <a href="mailto:aivancepro@gmail.com">aivancepro@gmail.com</a>. We comply with all data privacy regulations.</div></div>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Legal</h2>
      <ul>
          <li><a href="/en/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/en/terms/">Terms of Use</a></li>
      </ul>

      <a href="/en/" class="back">&larr; Back to home</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
